---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Fire Safety Resources & Compliance Guides | Property Managers & Contractors"
  description="Free fire safety compliance resources for property managers, facility managers, and fire protection contractors. NFPA checklists, buying guides, addressable vs conventional comparison, and more."
>
  <div class="section py-12">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-brand mb-2">Resources</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Fire Safety Resources & Guides</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-500 max-w-xl">Practical compliance guides, checklists, and buying resources for property managers, facility managers, and fire protection contractors.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Resource Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">

      <!-- PM Checklist -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">Property Managers</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Annual Fire Safety Compliance Checklist</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">A comprehensive annual checklist covering extinguisher inspections, alarm testing, sprinkler ITM, exit lighting, and documentation requirements for multi-family and commercial properties.</p>
        <a href="/resources/fire-safety-checklist-property-managers/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Addressable vs Conventional -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">Facility Managers</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Addressable vs. Conventional Fire Alarm Systems</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">A technical comparison guide for facility managers and engineers evaluating fire alarm system upgrades. Covers cost, scalability, AHJ requirements, and NFPA 72 compliance considerations.</p>
        <a href="/resources/addressable-vs-conventional-alarm-guide/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Commercial Retrofits -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">Contractors & FMs</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">2026 Commercial Fire Code Retrofit Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">What existing commercial buildings need to know about current retrofit requirements under NFPA 13, NFPA 72, and the IFC. Includes a state-by-state compliance snapshot.</p>
        <a href="/resources/commercial-fire-code-retrofits/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Extinguisher Buying Guide -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">Buying Guide</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Commercial Fire Extinguisher Buying Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">How to specify the right extinguisher for any commercial occupancy. Covers hazard classifications, agent types, size requirements, and NFPA 10 placement rules.</p>
        <a href="/resources/commercial-fire-extinguisher-guide/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Kitchen Suppression -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">Restaurant & Food Service</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">NFPA 96 Kitchen Suppression Compliance Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">Everything restaurant operators and property managers need to know about commercial kitchen hood suppression under NFPA 96. Inspection schedules, cleaning requirements, and system components.</p>
        <a href="/resources/nfpa-96-kitchen-suppression-guide/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Sprinkler ITM -->
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-brand mb-2">ITM Contractors</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Sprinkler System ITM Schedule Planner</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">A practical scheduling guide for fire sprinkler ITM contractors. Maps all NFPA 25 inspection and testing frequencies to a 12-month calendar with documentation checklists.</p>
        <a href="/resources/sprinkler-itm-schedule-planner/" class="text-sm font-medium text-red-brand hover:text-red-dark no-underline">Read guide &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Need equipment for a compliance project?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We supply wholesale fire protection equipment for contractors and facilities teams nationwide.</p>
      </div>
      <button onclick="openRFQ('','','Resources Page — Wholesale Inquiry')" class="bg-red-brand text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-red-dark transition-colors cursor-pointer border-0 whitespace-nowrap">Request Wholesale Pricing</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
